cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with developing a clustering approach to weed scouting using deep convolutional neural networks and robotics platform. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Robotics (cs.RO), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
